# Outlook / Microsoft Graph (for syncing contacts from your mailbox)
# Register an app at https://portal.azure.com/#view/Microsoft_AAD_RegisteredApps/ApplicationsListBlade
# 1. New registration → Name: "Vinny" (or any name)
# 2. Supported account types: "Accounts in any organizational directory and personal Microsoft accounts"
# 3. Redirect URI: Web → http://localhost:5173 (or your dev port)
# 4. API permissions → Add → Microsoft Graph → Delegated: User.Read, Mail.Read
# 5. Copy "Application (client) ID" below
VITE_AZURE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_AZURE_TENANT_ID=common
